data.description: Welcome to your best North Idaho life in this charming Kellogg home! Enjoy all that the mountains have to offer with endless recreation at your doorstep. Skiing, golfing, and a water park are close by. This home features tall ceilings on the main level, a delightful kitchen, and a welcoming front porch. Some areas of the home still have hardwood floors. It comes complete with a white picket fence and a low-maintenance yard. This home is ready for you to make yours!
